questions.explanation: Always edit existing files directly. Creating versioned or "improved" files violates ProjectTemplate core rules and creates confusion.
Root directory files must follow the allowlist in CLAUDE.md. Temporary files should go in appropriate subdirectories or be cleaned up immediately.
Reports belong in docs/reports/ directory. Root directory files must follow the strict allowlist.
